Interface AttachmentsCompat

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CorrectPackageNameAttachmentsCompat, WrongPackageNameAttachmentsCompat

    public interface AttachmentsCompat
    Wrapper interface that delegates operations to the real SendGrid Attchments object. This is needed since sendgrid-java has issue with generated packages.
